Inviting Purchasers
For each plot, an admin will need to invite the purchaser(s) to their personal Hoozzi portal:

Visit www.hoozzi.com/admin and enter your email address and password
Navigate to the development
Click the Phase tab and select the correct phase
Click on the plot
Click the Residents tab and then click Add Resident
Input the resident’s name, phone number and email address
Click Submit
Please note that the resident’s Hoozzi invite may be in their Junk Mail
You can add more than one resident to a single plot
You can add the same resident’s email to multiple plots

For each plot, you can assign a completion date, which will trigger a series of helpful emails sent to the resident in your company branding.
Navigate to the development
Click the Phase tab and select the correct phase
Click on the plot
Click the Completion tab
Enter or edit the completion date, then click Save Changes

Navigate back to a plot to delete/edit residents or update the completion date at any time.

